    {
      "locale": "ruRU",
      "text": "\"Мы не можем терять время в бою. Отправляемся в правый коридор\".",
      "modification_date": "2026-03-12T11:44:19.7528968Z",
      "traits": [
        {
          "trait": "CheckMe",
          "trait_date": "2025-11-27T10:54:46.3231353Z",
          "locale_text": "\"Себериан, без твоих умений гравитация нас уничтожит. Мы последуем за тобой\".",
          "speaker": "",
          "speaker_gender": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "locale": "enGB",
      "text": "\"We cannot waste our time fighting. Let us take the corridor on the right.\"",
      "modification_date": "2026-04-15T09:25:09.3800867Z",
      "translated_from": "ruRU",
      "translation_date": "2026-04-13T08:42:22.7201199Z",
      "original_text": "\"Мы не можем терять время в бою. Отправляемся в правый коридор\".",
      "traits": [
        {
          "trait": "Translated",
          "trait_date": "2026-04-13T08:42:22.7201215Z",
          "locale_text": "\"We cannot waste our time fighting. Let us head into the corridor on the right.\""
        },
        {
          "trait": "Edited",
          "trait_date": "2026-04-15T09:25:09.3800873Z",
          "locale_text": "\"We cannot waste our time fighting. Let us take the corridor on the right.\""
        },
        {
          "trait": "AD_tr_ed",
          "trait_date": "2026-01-20T07:38:26.9305304Z",
          "locale_text": "\"Seberian, without your skills, the gravity will destroy us. Lead us.\""
        },
